{"id":209587,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":29}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"453","ytitle":"","mtitle":"人民对你的希望","ftitle":"","authors":["唐剑鸣","肖景春"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔚蓝的一天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘浮着朵朵白云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从黑龙江到帕米尔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从漠河边到海南岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵延着无数的高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵横着千万条河川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋着无尽的宝藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着青葱的田园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我伟大祖国的领土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是多么宁静美丽!过去，这广阔的天空，飞过反动派的乌鸦，他们给人民制造灾难!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数的妻子哭着丈夫，无数的孩子失去了爹娘……人民记着这血海深仇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼望自己神鹰的生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晴空如洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的高空出现了神鹰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢翅上描绘着“八一”红星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人在向他欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民在向他招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们更抖起精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增强了解放台湾的信心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家欢笑了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑啊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为这是自己的神鹰!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的鹰:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你展开钢铁的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自由祖国的空中高翔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追噬那些害人的乌鸦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擒猎地上的灰兔黄鼠狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待台湾的人民欢笑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要张开你的锐爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫着祖国的边疆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁胆敢来侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就舞动你的锐爪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓出他们的眼睛和心脏!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(唐剑鸣)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁鸟在空中翱翔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出“隆隆”的回响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们仰首遥望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼你快快成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快展开那有力的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矫健地飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞啊!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过齐天的高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过辽阔的海洋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞到那渴待解放的地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(肖景春)"}]}